{"3585690": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Crown of Lust", "steam_appid": 3585690, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585690/extras/dc54eb019bda96562cc6521986a12baa.avif?t=1776032245\" width=568 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585690/extras/bbf0ff371f83bc8f26b8f59c3a8e2bba.poster.avif?t=1776032245\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585690/extras/bbf0ff371f83bc8f26b8f59c3a8e2bba.webm?t=1776032245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585690/extras/bbf0ff371f83bc8f26b8f59c3a8e2bba.mp4?t=1776032245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《慾望之冠》是一款奇幻成人視覺小說，背景設定在一個瀕臨崩潰的王國。當分隔正義王國瓦爾薩拉與腐化領域魯納里斯的古老帷幕開始破裂，戰爭的陰影籠罩在地平線之上。可惜的是，王國最後的希望，竟是一位寧願追女人也不願出席戰爭議會的風流王子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從小聽著魯納里人殘暴嗜血的恐怖故事長大，你抵達他們的邊境時，已做好面對最壞情況的準備……卻赫然發現，那些所謂的「野蠻人」，竟是一個由絕色美女所組成的王國——而她們對你那套皇室做派的不解，絲毫不亞於你對她們習俗的困惑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在危機四伏的異國宮廷中施展魅力、縱情誘惑，周旋於險象環生的政治陰謀之間，揭開一場蓄意將兩國拖入血腥戰爭的幕後黑手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585690/extras/ede5a6fc5d05a81d573e3ececc28dd56.avif?t=1776032245\" width=569 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・多重結局，取決於遊戲中的決定與選擇 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・多位可攻略的戀愛對象</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ・動態香艷場景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ・多語言翻譯